1
00:00:07,220 --> 00:00:11,820
♪She looks at the bright moon
hanging high above the clouds♪

2
00:00:11,860 --> 00:00:14,140
♪And I fall into the mountains♪

3
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:16,100
♪Protect this broken world♪

4
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:20,620
♪A faint wish♪

5
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:23,900
♪Life is just a dream,
isn't the world so?♪

6
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:27,620
♪Looking back,
I count the joys of my remaining years♪

7
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:31,020
♪It's difficult to see you in my dreams♪

8
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,940
♪Ignoring the coldness of the world,
I still linger♪

9
00:00:33,980 --> 00:00:37,300
♪Love and hate are intertwined,
not just in the past♪

10
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:40,900
♪The past is painful,
and time goes by in a flash♪

11
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:44,500
♪Stars fall on the mountain top again♪

12
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:48,140
♪My heart is as pure as the moon
and connected to you♪

13
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:56,980
[No One But You]

14
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:57,670
[Episode 4]

15
00:00:57,670 --> 00:01:01,980
[If we get snowed on together,
it counts as growing old together.]

16
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:06,820
[Zhongyi Hall]

17
00:01:34,820 --> 00:01:36,900
Is no one else
in the Military Governor's Mansion

18
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:38,740
or is Jiang Mohan afraid?

19
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:40,980
He actually let a woman come here

20
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,300
while he hides like a coward?

21
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:49,100
Not every insignificant nobody

22
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:51,260
is worthy of his personal time.

23
00:01:52,580 --> 00:01:53,340
My coming here

24
00:01:54,420 --> 00:01:56,020
is already flattering you.

25
00:01:56,420 --> 00:01:57,380
What did you say?

26
00:01:57,380 --> 00:01:58,220
Say that again!

27
00:02:04,980 --> 00:02:05,860
Second Uncle.

28
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:08,500
Since Miss Yu dared to come alone,

29
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:11,300
we Qing Gang should show some respect.

30
00:02:11,980 --> 00:02:13,140
Otherwise, if word gets out,

31
00:02:13,540 --> 00:02:15,500
our reputation will be damaged.

32
00:02:18,140 --> 00:02:19,980
I know an insider who is still alive.

33
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:21,340
I'll give you the address.

34
00:02:21,700 --> 00:02:22,940
You'll know when you get there.

35
00:02:26,780 --> 00:02:29,260
Jiang Mohan dares to fool us?

36
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:30,740
What?

37
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:35,060
You...

38
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:38,460
should know
the consequences of betraying me.

39
00:02:38,820 --> 00:02:40,860
I have never been threatened.

40
00:02:41,740 --> 00:02:43,780
The worst is
losing one more person's life.

41
00:02:45,220 --> 00:02:46,780
Am I really

42
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:48,180
just a tool to him?

43
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:49,220
- Kill her!
- He has gone too far!

44
00:02:49,220 --> 00:02:50,220
Kill her!

45
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:52,220
Don't be afraid, I'm here.

46
00:02:52,620 --> 00:02:53,620
It seems

47
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:56,100
that he didn't intend to let you
go back alive.

48
00:03:01,340 --> 00:03:02,940
Joys of Life

49
00:03:03,100 --> 00:03:06,740
is backed by the high-ranking officials
and dignitaries of the entire Beizhou.

50
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:09,180
Dare to touch me

51
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:12,100
and all your businesses, big and small,

52
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:14,020
will never have peace.

53
00:03:14,700 --> 00:03:16,300
Think about it carefully.

54
00:03:16,780 --> 00:03:17,980
Is doing this

55
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:19,220
worth it?

56
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:22,300
After going out this door,

57
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:24,660
I, Yu Qinghuan, will remember
the Qing Gang in a good light.

58
00:03:25,140 --> 00:03:27,060
But if you insist
on making things difficult for me,

59
00:03:27,380 --> 00:03:29,740
I will fight you to the death.

60
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:30,740
Stop!

61
00:03:33,340 --> 00:03:34,580
If I let this slide,

62
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:36,380
Qing Gang should
just change its surname to Jiang!

63
00:03:36,380 --> 00:03:38,380
The young leader dare not
take revenge for us,

64
00:03:38,380 --> 00:03:39,340
I dare!

65
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:50,220
You dare to hit me?

66
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:51,300
I'll kill you!

67
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:52,580
If something happens to me,

68
00:03:52,860 --> 00:03:55,780
my people
have thousands of ways to kill you.

69
00:03:55,780 --> 00:03:56,460
Fine!

70
00:03:57,060 --> 00:03:58,180
A life for a life.

71
00:03:58,180 --> 00:03:59,220
I'm not losing anything!

72
00:04:05,900 --> 00:04:07,300
My father is in a coma,

73
00:04:07,460 --> 00:04:08,620
not dead.

74
00:04:08,820 --> 00:04:10,660
I am still in charge here.

75
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:12,780
Do you not accept that?

76
00:04:13,980 --> 00:04:16,940
Young Leader, you've only been back
to the Qing Gang for a year.

77
00:04:17,380 --> 00:04:18,980
If you want to solidify your position,

78
00:04:18,980 --> 00:04:21,380
you have to ask your uncles and brothers
whether they agree.

79
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:24,380
Okay.

80
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:27,220
Who here refuses
to accept my leadership?

81
00:04:28,180 --> 00:04:29,100
Step forward.

82
00:04:29,260 --> 00:04:31,100
Don't blame me
for not giving you the chance.

83
00:05:09,980 --> 00:05:10,660
Come here.

84
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:36,660
I kept my promise and gave you gold.

85
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:40,380
How dare you hurt my woman?

86
00:05:41,060 --> 00:05:42,140
Looking to die?

87
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:45,100
It's a brick!

88
00:05:48,660 --> 00:05:50,300
I clearly gave you gold,

89
00:05:50,740 --> 00:05:52,100
but it turned into a brick.

90
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:57,460
That's your own problem.

91
00:06:00,580 --> 00:06:02,300
Sir, you're trying so hard
to find an excuse

92
00:06:02,660 --> 00:06:04,900
to seize the docks.

93
00:06:05,820 --> 00:06:08,140
You even
used someone close to you as a pawn.

94
00:06:08,740 --> 00:06:09,940
You are really malicious.

95
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:15,060
Better a pawn than a dead body.

96
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:18,580
Hahahaha.

97
00:06:19,700 --> 00:06:20,900
What are you doing?

98
00:06:20,900 --> 00:06:22,340
No need for the fight.

99
00:06:23,660 --> 00:06:26,380
Peace is the most important thing.

100
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:29,060
Pick a day. My treat.

101
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:32,860
We'll sit down and talk.

102
00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:34,660
Let's make money together.

103
00:06:37,340 --> 00:06:38,660
My Military Governor.

104
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,860
You're making quite a scene.

105
00:06:41,460 --> 00:06:42,820
It'll be difficult to wind this up.

106
00:06:46,740 --> 00:06:47,980
Put it away right now.

107
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:52,700
Retreat!

108
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:54,900
Wait!

109
00:06:58,300 --> 00:06:59,620
Which hand did he use to hit you?

110
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:01,700
His right hand.

111
00:07:20,300 --> 00:07:21,860
The game has just begun.

112
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:29,540
See you in the next round.

113
00:07:57,660 --> 00:07:58,380
Sprained your ankle?

114
00:07:58,940 --> 00:07:59,780
None of your business.

115
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:00,940
You...

116
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:02,940
I don't want to go back to my room.

117
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:36,740
♪Several springs have passed♪

118
00:08:37,180 --> 00:08:38,340
Your hair has gone grey.

119
00:08:38,340 --> 00:08:39,780
♪The old garden causes tears♪

120
00:08:41,980 --> 00:08:43,180
Your hair has gone grey too.

121
00:08:43,700 --> 00:08:46,980
♪Write and recite poems at night♪

122
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:50,500
"If we get snowed on together,

123
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:53,420
it counts as growing old together."

124
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:56,180
"If snow can replace growing old,

125
00:08:57,500 --> 00:08:59,500
there would not be
sad people in the world."

126
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:02,140
♪Years have gone by♪

127
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:05,860
♪Many times,
I sighed about when you were born♪

128
00:09:06,180 --> 00:09:08,860
♪I was not yet born♪

129
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:11,260
If I really died today,

130
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:13,140
you wouldn't care,

131
00:09:13,500 --> 00:09:14,380
right?

132
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:16,180
You're still useful to me.

133
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:19,020
How could I let you die?

134
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:22,780
♪It is a pity
that when you were born, I was not♪

135
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:26,700
♪Szechuan Lovage grows as time goes on♪

136
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:27,620
I got it.

137
00:09:28,300 --> 00:09:29,380
You said

138
00:09:29,780 --> 00:09:31,500
kindness will be repaid in full one day.

139
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:33,620
Before that,

140
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:35,500
I'll repay the kindness

141
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:37,220
and be your tool.

142
00:09:37,220 --> 00:09:41,140
♪My heart is for one person♪

143
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:43,940
♪Tears fall like the rain♪

144
00:09:44,100 --> 00:09:48,060
♪Strings are broken, words are silenced,
and the wind stops♪

145
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,980
[79 Jiangcun Road East]

146
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:08,900
I know an insider who is still alive.

147
00:10:09,260 --> 00:10:10,260
I'll give you the address.

148
00:10:10,540 --> 00:10:11,580
You'll know when you get there.

149
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:38,460
You're finally here.

150
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:40,340
I told you,

151
00:10:41,020 --> 00:10:42,420
do not try to hide anything from me.

152
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:45,860
You killed him.

153
00:11:05,580 --> 00:11:09,300
♪The waves♪

154
00:11:09,380 --> 00:11:13,580
♪When will you
stop looking through them?♪

155
00:11:13,660 --> 00:11:17,620
♪Missed the time
when the sun was restored♪

156
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:21,780
♪What else do you expect to like?♪

157
00:11:21,820 --> 00:11:24,540
♪I thought you were an angel♪

158
00:11:24,620 --> 00:11:26,840
♪An angel who watched over me♪

159
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:29,900
♪And saw every side of me♪

160
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:32,540
♪Until reality is flooded♪

161
00:11:32,620 --> 00:11:34,780
♪You become sensible♪

162
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:39,340
♪You are finally
out of touch with reality♪

163
00:11:39,650 --> 00:11:42,180
♪I hear the mountains, the seas,
and the people♪

164
00:11:42,260 --> 00:11:44,220
♪All clamoring because of you♪

165
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:46,300
♪Hiding in the cape after the rain♪

166
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:48,740
♪I cannot hear you♪

167
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:52,260
♪So I opened my arms one last time♪

168
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:55,780
♪But you escaped through the gap♪

169
00:11:55,890 --> 00:11:58,100
♪I saw winters come and summers go♪

170
00:11:58,140 --> 00:12:00,260
♪And thought there was ample time♪

171
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:02,300
♪Cannot withstand the waves♪

172
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:04,400
♪But you always make me panic♪

173
00:12:04,460 --> 00:12:08,700
♪How ridiculous, making me learn♪

174
00:12:08,780 --> 00:12:12,060
♪How much I am worth♪
